toscaModel:
tosca_definitions_version: tosca_simple_yaml_1_3

description: 

metadata:
  # The following fields are "normative" and expected in TOSCA 
  template_name: Cyango Cloud Studio - reimported
  template_author:  cyango-xr-developer
  template_version: ''

imports:
  - charity_custom_types_v08.yaml

topology_template:
  inputs:
  node_templates:
    charity-kafka:
      type: Charity.Component
      properties:
        name: charity-kafka
        deployment_unit: EXTERNAL
    AmazonS3:
      type: Charity.Component
      properties:
        name: amazons3
        deployment_unit: EXTERNAL
    cyango-backend:
      type: Charity.Component
      properties:
        name: cyango-backend
        deployment_unit: K8S_POD
        placement_hint: CLOUD
        image: repository.charity-project.eu/dotes/cyango-backend:production
      requirements:
        - host: cyango-backendNode
    cyango-backendNode:
      type: Charity.Node
      node_filter:
        capabilities:
          - host:
              properties:
                num_cpus: 
                  - equal: 0 
                mem_size: 
                  - greater_than: 0 MB
 
    cyango-database:
      type: Charity.Component
      properties:
        name: cyango-database
        deployment_unit: K8S_POD
        placement_hint: CLOUD
